Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.61,0:23:53.74,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Mind’s eye flickers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:56.46,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}もう一人の自分にグッバイ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:23:58.19,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}We are Drifters
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.80,0:22:38.83,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}去实现于天空彼方的约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.97,0:22:46.46,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我祈愿与你并肩前行
Comment: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:48.57,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Beautiful it’s beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.98,0:22:53.27,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}正确与否
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.27,0:22:55.62,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}只取决于自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.84,0:23:03.49,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}时而莫衷一是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:10.40,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}时而词不达意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:12.46,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}这也无可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.46,0:23:15.92,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}让弱小的我变得强大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:21.47,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}是为与你相称
Comment: 0,0:23:24.41,0:23:25.95,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}I ain’t fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.95,0:23:27.95,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我难以割舍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:32.44,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}亦如无法放弃
Comment: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:34.31,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Keeping promises
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.31,0:23:35.94,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}既然立下誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.94,0:23:39.28,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我将在彼方守候
Comment: 0,0:23:39.28,0:23:40.48,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}I meant for you
Comment: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:41.70,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}We are Drifters
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.70,0:23:44.64,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}直达内心
Comment: 0,0:23:44.64,0:23:45.64,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Mind’s eye flickers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.64,0:23:48.73,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}拥抱仅剩的两日
Comment: 0,0:23:48.73,0:23:49.88,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}We are Drifters
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.88,0:23:52.61,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我的决心矢志不渝
